it is adding or substracting matrices from the image

M = np.ones(image.shape , "uint8") * 75
added = cv2.add(image,M)  ---> image becomes darker
substracted = cv2.substract(image,M)  ---> image becomes lighter



Bitwise Operations:

or = bitwise_or(img1,img2)
and = bitwise_and(img1,img2)
xor = bitwise_xor(img1,img2)
not = bitwise_not(img1)